1 KAPPA_Version_1.1

   A new release of KAPPA (v1.1) has been made. The main changes are:

   - Initial support for spectral world coordinate systems (see WCSADD,
   LINPLOT, etc). This includes flexible conversion between different
   units, spectral systems and reference frames.

   For complete details of all changes, see the "Release Notes" appendix in 
   SUN/95. 

